com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.handlers

Class SCUIXAPIMashupLeafMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.handlers.SCUIXAPIMashupLeafMetaData

  • public class SCUIXAPIMashupLeafMetaData
extends java.lang.Object
    SCUIXAPIMashupLeafMetaData class contains metadata for all the leaf mashups in the aggregate mashup or individual mashup in case of single XAPI calls. The leaf mashup contains the details of the actual XAPI call like Input, Template etc. This is used by SCUIXAPIAggregatorMashupHandler to flatten the aggregate mashup and cache the flattened list of leaf mashup metadata. The object for this class will not change per request. This is also used by SCUIXAPIMashupHandler to store XAPI mashup related meta data. rasrinivasan
